ied the withdrawal procedure ➢ Required outstanding invoices to be \nsubmitted by a date certain and only after ... Transmission Expansion and Interconnection Manual | ix\n➢ Clarified treatment of a deposit in lieu of Site Control for Large Facilities,\n➢ Added requirement to perform preliminary, non-binding deliverability evaluation in SRIS \nand associated revisions,\n➢ Modified analyses performed in the SRIS and Class Year Study stages to eliminate \nduplicative and unnecessary analysis,\n➢ Modified the Class Year Study entry procedures,\n➢"
